Class DirectMessage.ChatListItem

java.lang.Object
application.DirectMessage.ChatListItem
Enclosing class:
DirectMessage
private static class DirectMessage.ChatListItem extends Object
Inner class to represent a chat list item.

This class encapsulates information about a chat including the chat ID, other user's username, last message, timestamp, and unread status.
